<!doctype html>
<html lang="en-GB">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
<title>Contact Us — Emmanuel Church, West Hampstead</title>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" />
<style>
  .ct-contactcard { background:#fff; border:1px solid var(--line); padding:34px 34px 36px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:24px; }
  .ct-line { display:flex; gap:18px; align-items:flex-start; }
  .ct-line .ic { width:42px; height:42px; flex-shrink:0; border:1px solid var(--line); background:var(--cream); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; color:var(--brown); }
  .ct-line .ic svg { width:20px; height:20px; stroke:currentColor; stroke-width:1.5; fill:none; }
  .ct-line .k { font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:11px; font-weight:var(--fw-bold); letter-spacing:0.2em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--brown); margin-bottom:5px; }
  .ct-line .v { font-family:var(--font-display); font-size:21px; color:var(--ink); line-height:1.3; }
  .ct-line .v a { color:var(--ink); text-decoration:none; }
  .ct-line .v a:hover { color:var(--brown); }
  .ct-line .v small { display:block; font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:14px; color:var(--muted); margin-top:3px; }
  .ct-travel { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:0; }
  .ct-travel .col { padding:40px 44px; }
  .ct-travel .col:first-child { border-right:1px solid var(--line); padding-left:0; }
  .ct-travel .col:last-child { padding-right:0; }
  .ct-travel .head { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:14px; margin-bottom:24px; }
  .ct-travel .head .ic { width:46px; height:46px; color:var(--brown); }
  .ct-travel .head .ic svg { width:100%; height:100%; stroke:currentColor; stroke-width:1.4; fill:none; }
  .ct-travel .head h3 { font-family:var(--font-display); font-size:28px; font-weight:var(--fw-semibold); color:var(--navy); margin:0; }
  .ct-route { padding:18px 0; border-top:1px solid var(--line); }
  .ct-route:last-child { border-bottom:1px solid var(--line); }
  .ct-route .rt { font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:11px; font-weight:var(--fw-bold); letter-spacing:0.16em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--brown); margin-bottom:7px; display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:6px; }
  .ct-route .rt b { background:var(--navy); color:#fff; padding:2px 8px; border-radius:var(--radius-sm); font-weight:var(--fw-bold); letter-spacing:0.04em; }
  .ct-route p { font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:15px; line-height:1.55; color:var(--ink-soft); margin:0; }
  .ct-route p b { color:var(--ink); font-weight:var(--fw-semibold); }
</style>
</head>
<body>

{% include "header.njk" %}

  <section class="em-pagehead em-pagehead--band">
    <div class="inner">
      <div class="em-breadcrumb"><a href="index.html">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><span>Contact Us</span></div>
      <h1>Contact <em>us</em></h1>
      <p class="deck">If you would like to request a prayer for yourself or someone else, or to contact us about any other matter, please reach the clergy via the Parish Office below.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Office details + prayer note -->
  <section class="em-intro">
    <div class="inner">
      <div class="em-body">
        <p class="em-lead">Whatever is on your heart — a prayer request, a question, or simply wanting to get in touch — we would be glad to hear from you.</p>
        <p>The clergy can be reached through the Parish Office, and we aim to respond as soon as we are able. If your enquiry concerns a baptism, wedding or funeral, do let us know and we will pass it to the right person.</p>
        <p>You are always welcome to come and find us in person, too — before or after any of our services, or by arranging a time to visit the church and the Nazareth Chapel for quiet prayer.</p>
        <h3>Join our email list and newsletter</h3>
        <p>If you'd like to join our email list — which includes receiving our regular newsletter — please <a href="https://emmanuelnw6.us9.list-manage.com/subscribe?u=82a1a8e47d9788dccae693588&id=bbf2ae4052" target="_blank" rel="noopener">click here</a>. We send updates fortnightly, with news, service times and what's coming up across the parish.</p>
      </div>
      <aside class="em-aside">
        <div class="ct-contactcard">
          <div class="ct-line">
            <span class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg></span>
            <div><div class="k">Address</div><div class="v">Emmanuel Church<small>Lyncroft Gardens, London NW6 1JU</small></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="ct-line">
            <span class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.13.96.36 1.9.7 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.91.34 1.85.57 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg></span>
            <div><div class="k">Phone</div><div class="v"><a href="tel:+447751534297">07751 534 297</a></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="ct-line">
            <span class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2"/><path d="m22 6-10 7L2 6"/></svg></span>
            <div><div class="k">Email the Parish Office</div><div class="v"><a href="mailto:info@emmanuelnw6.com">info@emmanuelnw6.com</a></div></div>
          </div>
          <a href="mailto:info@emmanuelnw6.com" class="em-btn em-btn--primary" style="justify-content:center; margin-top:2px">Request a prayer</a>
        </div>
        <div class="em-aside-card" style="margin-top:24px">
          <h4>Office hours</h4>
          <p>The clergy are part-time and respond to messages as soon as they can. For urgent pastoral or safeguarding matters, please call and leave a message.</p>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Getting here -->
  <section class="em-section em-section--band">
    <div class="inner">
      <div class="em-sectionhead">
        <div class="em-ornament is-leading">Finding us</div>
        <h2>How to get to <em>Emmanuel</em></h2>
        <p class="em-lead">The church sits at the heart of West Hampstead, close to the village green and well served by bus and rail.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ct-travel">
        <div class="col">
          <div class="head">
            <span class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M8 6v6"/><path d="M16 6v6"/><path d="M2 12h20"/><path d="M18 18h1a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-6a8 8 0 0 0-8-8H9a8 8 0 0 0-8 8v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h1"/><path d="M9 18h6"/><circle cx="7" cy="18" r="2"/><circle cx="17" cy="18" r="2"/></svg></span>
            <h3>By bus</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="ct-route">
            <div class="rt"><b>139</b><b>328</b><b>C11</b></div>
            <p>Into the heart of West Hampstead. Alight at the <b>West End Green</b> stop.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="ct-route">
            <div class="rt"><b>82</b><b>13</b><b>113</b></div>
            <p>Along the Finchley Road. Alight at the <b>Lyncroft Gardens</b> stop.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col">
          <div class="head">
            <span class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="4" y="3" width="16" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M4 11h16"/><path d="M8 21l2-3"/><path d="M16 21l-2-3"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="14" r="0.5"/><circle cx="15.5" cy="14" r="0.5"/></svg></span>
            <h3>By rail</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="ct-route">
            <div class="rt"><b>Jubilee Line</b> · Zone 2</div>
            <p>West Hampstead — <b>turn right</b> out of the station.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="ct-route">
            <div class="rt"><b>London Overground</b></div>
            <p>West Hampstead — <b>turn left</b> out of the station.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="ct-route">
            <div class="rt"><b>Thameslink</b></div>
            <p>West Hampstead — <b>turn left</b> out of the station on the West End Lane exit. From the Iverson Road ticket office, turn left and left again onto West End Lane.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Map -->
  <section class="em-section">
    <div class="inner">
      <div class="em-well" style="aspect-ratio:21/8">
        <div class="em-img-placeholder"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="8.5" r="1.5"/><polyline points="21 15 16 10 5 21"/></svg></div>
